window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Can you imagine writing to Father Christmas and actually getting a reply? </p> <p>Every year, the children of J.R.R. Tolkien would write to Father Christmas, and the letters they received told wonderful stories of his adventures at the North Pole. </p> <p>These humorous tales are brought to life by Derek Jacobi as Father Christmas, John Moffatt as Polar Bear, and Christian Rodska as Ilbereth the Elf, complete with specially composed music.</p>"; 
